SUB_W03_EVAR_AMYA_SLOTH_HELP_000_CUT_010.text:
Er, I meeean...he hates noise! I don't know
if you could call it a weakness, exactly,
but loud noises send him right to sleep.

SUB_W03_EVAR_AMYA_ALL_SLOTH_NOTHING_000_.text:
Blast! The key's right next to his pillow;
I don't think we can grab it without
waking him in the process.

SUB_W03_EVAR_AMYA_BABY_RUIN_000_CUT_000_.text:
I am the Dismal King;
naught transpires in Yomi
that I do not know of.

SUB_W03_EVAR_AMYA_BABY_SLOTH_100_CUT_000.text:
My thralls have cleared the way;
we need not go to the trouble of
meeting the Warden of Sloth.

SUB_W03_EVAR_AMYA_BABY_LUST_100_CUT_000_.text:
My thralls have cleared the way;
we need not go to the trouble of
meeting the Warden of Lust.

SUB_W03_EVAR_AMYA_BABY_GLUTTONY_100_CUT_.text:
My thralls have cleared the way;
we need not go to the trouble of
meeting the Warden of Gluttony.

SUB_W03_EVAR_AMYA_BABY_LUST_000_CUT_000_.text:
A king is a supreme being;
one not bound by concepts like
responsibility or freedom.

SUB_W03_EVAR_AMYA_BABY_GRAVEYARD_100_CUT.text:
Well, I don't think there's anyone
else around to get in our way,
so let's get going, King!
